Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?feat:=20checklist=20de=20jogos/t=C3=A9cnicas=20?=
 =?UTF-8?q?na=20chamada=20e=20detalhe=20da=20t=C3=A9cnica=20em=20modal?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
